constructor.description: Initializes the contract with a logic address, admin address, and optional initialization data.

changeAdmin.description: Changes the admin address to a new address.

upgradeTo.description: Upgrades the contract to a new implementation address.

upgradeToAndCall.description: Upgrades the contract to a new implementation address and calls a function in the new implementation.

AdminChanged.description: Emitted when the admin address is changed.

BeaconUpgraded.description: Emitted when the beacon address is upgraded.

Upgraded.description: Emitted when the implementation address is upgraded.
